---
title: Crispy Tofu & Southeast Asian Coconut Sauce with Veggies, Garlic Rice & Peanuts
description: Our firm tofu is coated in cornflour for ultimate crispiness when cooked. Then, we've teamed it with a dazzling
coconut sauce made using Sri Lankan-style spices, plus steamed rice flavoured with fragrant garlic. When you serve
this up, everyone will be singing your praises!
